182
00:12:02,226 --> 00:12:03,066
Co děláš, Nano?

183
00:12:03,519 --> 00:12:03,989
Jdeme.

184
00:12:04,845 --> 00:12:05,070
Dobře.

185
00:12:06,670 --> 00:12:07,297
